<p>Note: if your blog&#8217;s web address changes (for example, owing to the shutdown of Typepad) you can request to have the link to your blog updated on this list, either in the comments or via <a href="mailto:dailynouseditor@gmail.com">email</a>.</p><p>The post <a href="https://dailynous.com/2025/09/18/the-philosophy-blogosphere-in-2025/">The Philosophy Blogosphere in 2025</a> first appeared on <a href="https://dailynous.com">Daily Nous</a>.</p>